name: ooMEFBrowser
tagline: Matlab GUI for reading MEF formatted EEG files
body:
# ooMEFBrowser
Matlab GUI for reading MEF formatted EEG files

ooMEFBrowser is a MATLAB(tm) GUI created to open and display MEF formatted EEG files. It supports basic functionality tailored to EEG analysis.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
